QuestData.Title: Report to Oribos
QuestData.Description:
Ardenweald has withstood the unrelenting force of the Maw.
But it was still not enough.
Return to our allies in Oribos. There must be an answer for this loss, and action taken.
QuestData.RewardText:
The Jailer has begun his attack on Oribos.
What I have feared the most has come to pass.
